msgctxt "56_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Hi, Mom. It's been a while."
msgstr "Hola, Mamá... Cuánto tiempo sin verte."

msgctxt "68_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Why haven't you contacted us!? And who is this young man with you?"
msgstr "¡Qué barbaridad! Ni siquiera te molestas en llamar, eres tan... Oh, ¿y quién es el caballero?"

msgctxt "80_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "This is my boyfriend, Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr "Ah, él es mi novio, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "92_Kiryu"
msgid "Boyfriend? Uh, I mean, hello, ma'am. I'm Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr "¿Novio...? Eh... me llamo Kazuma Kiryu. Un placer."

msgctxt "116_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Hello. I'm Hiyori's mother."
msgstr "Mucho gusto. Soy la madre de Hiyori."

msgctxt "176_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Wow, Hiyori. Kiryu-san's quite a catch. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I'd say he's the spitting image of your father when he was young! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Uy, Hiyori! Kiryu-san es muy apuesto. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¡Es la viva imagen de tu padre cuando era joven! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "188_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "What are you talking about!? He looks nothing like Dad! Don't lump Kiryu-san in with that jerk!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué dices?! ¡No se parece nada a papá! ¡No compares a Kiryu-san con ese cretino!"

msgctxt "200_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Hiyori... Don't you think it's time you forgave your father?"
msgstr "Hiyori... ¿No crees que ya es hora de que perdones a tu padre?"

msgctxt "212_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "He may have gone a little too far, but he only did it because he was just worried about you..."
msgstr "Puede que se haya pasado un poco, pero igual se preocupa por ti..."

msgctxt "224_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "236_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Besides, you may have heard about this, but..."
msgstr "Y además... quizá ya lo hayas escuchado por ahí, pero..."

msgctxt "248_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Kamuro Pro Wrestling isn't doing very well."
msgstr "Kamuro Pro Wrestling está en la cuerda floja..."

msgctxt "260_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "What!? What's going on!?"
msgstr "¡¿Eh!? ¡¿Qué quieres decir!?"

msgctxt "272_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "The mixed martial arts craze has been hard on professional wrestling. Customers aren't as frequent as before. And in this economy..."
msgstr "Con el auge de las artes marciales mixtas, ya no tenemos tantos clientes como antes... y para colmo, con esta crisis económica..."

msgctxt "284_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "He's had trouble getting loans from banks, so I think he's been dealing with some shady characters."
msgstr "Como el banco no le negó el préstamo, parece que tu padre tuvo que pedir dinero a gente de dudosa reputación..."

msgctxt "296_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Oh no... I had no idea..."
msgstr "Oh no... No tenía idea..."

msgctxt "308_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "If he can't get more customers soon, he'll have no way to pay back the loan sharks..."
msgstr "Si no consigue más clientes pronto, no va a tener cómo pagar a los prestamistas..."

msgctxt "320_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Men have been coming to the house looking for money... I don't know what to do anymore."
msgstr "Últimamente, vienen hombres a la casa por dinero... Ya no sé qué más hacer."

msgctxt "332_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "This has all been very hard on your father especially with you gone."
msgstr "Todo esto ha sido muy duro para tu padre, especialmente desde que te fuiste."

msgctxt "344_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "356_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "He made me promise not to tell you any of this, but I thought you should know."
msgstr "Tu padre me pidió que no te contara nada de esto, pero pensé que era mejor que lo supieras."

msgctxt "368_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Ya veo..."

msgctxt "380_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "That said, you shouldn't worry about the money. I've started working part-time to help out."
msgstr "En fin, no te preocupes por el dinero. Yo también conseguí un trabajo de medio tiempo."

msgctxt "392_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Are you still going to college?"
msgstr "¿Estás yendo a la universidad como siempre?"

msgctxt "404_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "Yes..."
msgstr "Sí..."

msgctxt "416_Hiyori's Mother"
msgid "Remember, if you're going to be a teacher, you have to study hard to make that dream come true."
msgstr "Recuerda, si quieres ser profesora, tienes que estudiar mucho para que ese sueño se cumpla."

msgctxt "428_松岡里緒奈：源氏名"
msgid "I know..."
msgstr "Lo sé..."

